title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Afters with ‘Industry’ Co-Creators Mickey Down and Konrad Kay
description:
On our new weekly lightning round mini ep with ‘Industry’ Co-Creators Mickey Down and Konrad Kay, we’re fucking around with personal style, Hollywood’s dubious track record, all time TV, Industry season 2, partying, the Emmy Awards, tales from Berghain, actors and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
